title: The Illiance - Under The Bridge
description:
The Illiance - Under The Bridge

Defunct hip hop group out of Detroit. Now some of the group members are a part of Detroit CYDI and also the rapper Stryfe Da Fantam.

From around 2004, probably earlier than that.
